<br>
I personally use a Fleshgrinder mainhand, and a Flaming Dirk (which btw is inproperly listed in Magelo, in actuality it has 3 fire dmg) offhand.  When I encounter mobs with high FR, I swap out to a Frostbringer mainhand, Snowchipper offhand.  There are alot of other variables that come into play, such as buffs that greatly effect which weapons you should choose.  Have max dex? throw in procers.  Crap dex but maxed str? best ratio will probably be your best choice.  So the bottom line is, experiment with them and use different weapons depending on the situation.<br>
<br>
This of course is assuming you want agro.  If you arent MA obviously you want to try to avoid procs and maximize damage, and obviously nothing says lovin quite like a solid 2 hander in this department <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p><br><center>
